items.title: NUTSO x DANSE- 100 DEEP
items.description:
DANSE and NUTSO linked up to flip this classic MOBB DEEP track which originally featured NAS.  This is one of the rare times we see DANSE collab with someone outside of his BKLYN STICKUP click.  They both deliver impressive, grimey, picture perfect verses and as always- the artwork is on point.

NUTSO- @NUTSOPPM
DANSE- @BKLYNSTICKUP
